ent-WeaponDrakeIndustrialCutter = Drake industrial cutter
    .desc = Drake Industries proto-kinetic cutter. Runs on a tank of gaseous plasma. Rated for rock, wreckage, and supercompacted asteroid walls.

ent-WeaponDrakeIndustrialGrenadeLauncher = Drake industrial grenade launcher
    .desc = Drake Industries three-round launcher for standard seismic charges. Fired accurately when wielded with both hands.

ent-WeaponDrakeIndustrialLaser = Drake industrial laser
    .desc = Drake Industries mining laser with plasma tank and internal cell. Two-handed. Clears rock and relocates mined ore to the operator.

ent-DrakeIndustrialOreBag = Drake industrial ore bag
    .desc = Enlarged Drake Industries sack for ore and artifact fragments.

ent-DrakeIndustrialConstructionBag = Drake industrial construction bag
    .desc = Enlarged Drake Industries construction bag for sheets and building materials.

ent-JetpackDrakeIndustrial = Drake industrial jetpack
    .desc = Drake Industries void jetpack with an enlarged fuel reservoir. The tank supplies thrust only — use a separate oxygen source for breathing.

ent-JetpackDrakeIndustrialFilled = Drake industrial jetpack
    .desc = { ent-JetpackDrakeIndustrial.desc }

ent-ClothingShoesBootsMagDrakeIndustrial = Drake industrial magboots
    .desc = Drake Industries magboots with a side knife mount. Reduced movement penalty.
